feature.label: IPC (Multicore and I/O) (Target Content)
feature.description: This version of IPC (Multicore and I/O) Target Content can be chosen separatly for each C/C++ project via their project settings. The IPC (Multicore and I/O) IDE Client, on the other hand, is common to all projects and its version must be equal to or greater than the version of this Target Content feature.
